WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:03.300
It was you who insisted that his mother give birth to him

2
00:00:03.333 --> 00:00:04.800
I sent him abroad

3
00:00:04.800 --> 00:00:07.300
It's up to you to bring him back

4
00:00:07.400 --> 00:00:10.033
That's your son!

5
00:00:10.666 --> 00:00:14.000
Did I give birth to this beast so that he could bite me back?

6
00:00:14.133 --> 00:00:16.666
Did you raise him for a day?

7
00:00:16.666 --> 00:00:19.300
You've been spending the rest of your life

8
00:00:19.300 --> 00:00:21.366
Eat, drink, gamble

9
00:00:21.366 --> 00:00:24.200
The only right thing you've done for half your life

10
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:27.033
Just gave birth to a dad

11
00:00:27.166 --> 00:00:29.100
I'm your son

12
00:00:29.466 --> 00:00:30.966
Would you like to help Tinlan

13
00:00:31.066 --> 00:00:34.366
Even helping an outsider won't help me?

14
00:00:34.366 --> 00:00:37.500
I've told you since that incident three years ago

15
00:00:37.566 --> 00:00:39.300
Let's sever the father-son relationship

16
00:00:39.333 --> 00:00:41.000
I don't have you as my son

17
00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:44.366
Why do you want to help that kid?

18
00:00:44.366 --> 00:00:47.233
I am the heir to the Shen family

19
00:00:48.366 --> 00:00:49.666
It's all mine

20
00:00:49.766 --> 00:00:51.166
It's all mine.

21
00:00:53.866 --> 00:00:55.300
Let go

22
00:01:00.066 --> 00:01:00.866
young master

23
